WEBVTT

00:03:27.255 --> 00:03:32.182
As much as has been raped away from our people

00:03:32.182 --> 00:03:36.121
How can you expect me to treat
their imprint on your language

00:03:36.121 --> 00:03:38.735
As anything less than equal

00:03:38.735 --> 00:03:40.607
Let there be no confusion

00:03:40.607 --> 00:03:42.421
Let there be no hesitation

00:03:42.421 --> 00:03:44.485
This is not a promotion of ignorance

00:03:44.485 --> 00:03:47.930
This is a linguistic celebration

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:53.009
That’s why I put "tri-lingual" on my last job application

00:03:53.009 --> 00:03:55.740
I can help to diversify your consumer market

00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:57.372
is all I wanted them to know

00:03:57.372 --> 00:03:59.105
And when they call me for the interview

00:03:59.105 --> 00:04:00.615
I’ll be more than happy to show that